{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Sebastian Klingler | Front-end Engineer","author":"Sebastian Klingler"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"d4e70f46-b667-5f1f-9a04-f630cdaed7ca","html":"<p><a href=\"http://www.hallpass.io/\">Hallpass</a> is a password manager focused on security via biometrics. It allows users to sign in to websites on any device by using the fingerprint sensor on their phone.</p>\n<h2>Motivation</h2>\n<p>Hallpass was conceived of at <a href=\"https://www.hackdfw.com/\">Hack-DFW</a> 2016 as a way to consolidate password management without having to rely on a master password. It uses AES-256 encryption and supports authorizing and deauthorizing multiple devices for each user.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/hallpass-de616b663462e6df3b8d3b51aa6c804d-c0a33.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 518px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 178.57142857142856%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Hallpass\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/hallpass-de616b663462e6df3b8d3b51aa6c804d-c0a33.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/hallpass-de616b663462e6df3b8d3b51aa6c804d-2fdb2.png 148w,\n/static/hallpass-de616b663462e6df3b8d3b51aa6c804d-ece9d.png 295w,\n/static/hallpass-de616b663462e6df3b8d3b51aa6c804d-c0a33.png 518w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 518px) 100vw, 518px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<h2>Stack</h2>\n<h3>Backend</h3>\n<p><a href=\"\">Node.js</a> in combination with <a href=\"\">socket.io</a> was used to build the api and support push/pull connections.</p>\n<p><a href=\"\">MongoDB</a> was used for efficient data retrieval</p>\n<h3>Frontend</h3>\n<p><a href=\"\">Kotlin</a> was used to develop the native Android app\n<a href=\"\">Swift</a> was used to develop the native iOS app</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Hallpass","date":"January 07, 2017"}}},"pageContext":{"jsonName":"hallpass-7ee","internalComponentName":"ComponentHallpass","path":"/Hallpass/","component":"/Users/sebastian/workspace/sliptype.github.io/src/templates/blog-post.js","componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","context":{"slug":"/Hallpass/","previous":null,"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/tacky/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Tacky"}}},"updatedAt":1530839653033,"pluginCreator___NODE":"Plugin default-site-plugin","pluginCreatorId":"Plugin default-site-plugin","componentPath":"/Users/sebastian/workspace/sliptype.github.io/src/templates/blog-post.js","slug":"/Hallpass/","previous":null,"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/tacky/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Tacky"}}}}